{"tid":1803903,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【工會post】一月一日大遊行音樂人工會街站","createTime":"2019-12-30T14:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T06:51:35.000Z","uid":45858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55711d379cc18931af01838abdd870887a214c1b","tid":1803903,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHszpqH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHszpqH.jpg&h=7dcc42e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 月1 日元旦大遊行音樂人工會街站<br />\n時間：12點<br />\n地點：修頓球場<br />\n<br />\n香港音樂人工會，主要由一群關心音樂行業發展及權益的音樂人組成。為職工盟轄下的其中一個分會，總會為 &lt;個人及社區服務行業職工總會&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n本會主要關注香港音樂從業員的權益包括薪酬待遇，工作環境， 和主力協助處理音樂行業的勞資糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n除咗為同業發聲外，我哋都想藉機會，集合香港所有為自由而發聲嘅音樂人，籌備業工運抗爭，為各行業三罷注入更大力量。<br />\n<br />\n不要散水撚，只要團結，三罷不是夢。<br />\n<br />\n音樂界同路人三罷tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/musicworker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmusicworker&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=c0715630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/musicworker</a><br />\n音樂人工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKMuIN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKMuIN&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=1ff3a758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKMuIN</a> <br />\n音樂街站義工群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/musichelper2327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmusichelper2327&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=9be164ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/musichelper2327</a><br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rBzKUq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rBzKUq&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=fe8c04d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rBzKUq</a>"},{"pid":"74a7304b1581864f92f8a080230e39afb7eeef46","tid":1803903,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy